1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:12,000
L3AI opens with a public demo-first experience for Web3 decision context.

2
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:27,000
Visitors choose the right path before opening files: customer, partner, investor, media or launch operator.

3
00:00:27,000 --> 00:00:45,000
The AI Quant workflow is explained as research context and structured reasoning, not trading certainty.

4
00:00:45,000 --> 00:01:03,000
Wallet-aware journeys help explain context, verification and audit checkpoints without exposing private wallet data.

5
00:01:03,000 --> 00:01:21,000
The business presentation gives reviewers the model, roadmap, launch assets and claim guardrails.

6
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:39,000
The Launch Experience Center collects the whitepaper, deck, demo package, video package and manifests.

7
00:01:39,000 --> 00:01:52,000
FAQ content keeps advice boundaries, risk notes and public wording clear.

8
00:01:52,000 --> 00:02:00,000
L3AI is ready for controlled external review through the public showcase and resource center.
